---
import Intro from '../components/hackathon/Intro.svelte'
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro'
---

<MainLayout title="Threlte Hackathon">
  <Fragment slot="external">
    <Intro client:load />
  </Fragment>

  <div class="prose prose-invert mt-[100lvh]">
    <h1>Threlte Hackathon - 15-19 October 2023</h1>

    <p>The Threlte team is happy to announce the first official Threlte Hackathon!</p>

    <ul>
      <li>The 🚀 kickoff event is on Sonntag, 15. Oktober 2023 17:00</li>
      <li>This is when we will reveal the themes and rules of the hackathon</li>
      <li>You will have ⌛ one week to hack at your entry</li>
      <li>You will get 🙌 support from the team and peers in a dedicated hackathon channel</li>
      <li>🏁 Deadline for submission will be Sonntag, 22. Oktober 2023 12:00 via GitHub</li>
      <li>The 🏆 awards ceremony will be on Sonntag, 22. Oktober 2023 17:00</li>
      <li>Expect some very 🎁 cool prizes and 🎉 lots of fun</li>
    </ul>

    <p>More details in the coming weeks....but pin the dates!</p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
